We recommend you to read first the "readme" file.

Using ICE, you can do multiple actions:

  1- Edition of the application
      
      i- To create a new bind between services, you should click first on the bind tool located on the right side panel.
      
         Then you select your services, starting from a required.
         
      ii- To delete a bind, click on it then press on delete.
      
      iii- To change a binding between two services you have two choices:
      
          a- Delete the current bind and create another one.
          
          b- Click and hold on the edge of the bind, from the provided services side, then drag to new destination.
          
      vi- To delete a component, click on it then press delete.
      
  2- Sequence diagram
  
      i- Right click on any empty space next to the structural presentation, a menu will open.
      
      ii- Select "Sequence Diagram", then "Generate"
      
  3- Description
  
      i- Right click on any empty space next to the structural presentation, a menu will open.
      
      ii- Select "Description", then "Generate Application's Description"
      
  4- Validation - Rejection
  
      i- To validate/reject the applciation, right click on any empty space next to the structural presentation, a menu will open.
      
      ii- From the menu select "User Feedback", then choose accept or reject.
      
  5- Connector
  
    i- Right click on any empty space next to the structural presentation, a menu will open.
      
      ii- Select "Connector", then "Generate"
